data.description: Wow! This beautiful 4-bedroom home has been lovingly updated and maintained by the current owners and is move-in ready. Recent updates include the roof & siding (2019), all windows (2018), the furnace (2022), the air conditioner (2021), new flooring in the entry, hall, powder room, & kitchen (2023), new hinges and interior door knobs (2023), and fresh interior paint (2023). Engineered hardwood flooring flows through the living and dining rooms and large windows let in abundant light. The generously sized family room is open to the eat-in kitchen, updated in 2015 with new counters and cabinets. The black appliances are all newer including the stove (2015), refrigerator (2017), microwave (2021), and dishwasher (2016). Upstairs you will find 4 bedrooms, including the primary bedroom and attached bath. The owners updated all bathrooms in 2018 with granite counters and new toilets. The lower level features a large rec room and a utility room. This home has plenty of storage space including a large crawl space. Relax and unwind on the covered front porch or on the large rear deck. The shed in the backyard offers additional storage space and has a newer roof (2019). All you have to do is place your furniture!
